metadata.dc:description: Ten cases of the paranasal sinuses mucoceles are reported. We analyse their incidence, localization, presentation symptoms and signs, treatment, operative and pathological findings.
metadata.dc:title: Mucoceles: estudio retrospectivo y aportación de nuestra experiencia.
[Mucocele: a retrospective study and presentation of our experience].
